Shino sends his [[Kikaichū|insects]] to encase the opponent; the insects then lift the opponent into the air, and crush them.

== Trivia ==
* This technique works in a way similar to [[Gaara]]'s two signature techniques, [[Sand Binding Coffin]] and [[Sand Waterfall Funeral]], with the insects acting as Gaara's [[sand]].
